  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要把BloodHound分析出来的Alice攻击路径可视化一下。核心是想展示从域用户到工作站的权限关系，还有容器层级结构。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ALICE",
        "LAPTOP",
        "PHANTOM",
        "DOMAINUSERS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，是要做横向布局对吧？我注意到Alice对她的笔记本有AdminTo权限，同时她是Domain Users成员。这两个关系都要画出来？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ALICE",
        "LAPTOP",
        "DOMAINUSERS",
        "AdminTo",
        "MemberOf"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，这两个都是关键攻击路径。另外还要把AD的容器层级加上——Users容器包含Alice，Phantom.Corp域又包含Users容器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USERS",
        "PHANTOM",
        "Contains"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，主体结构有了。现在给不同节点类型做颜色区分：用户用蓝色系，工作站用橙色，组用绿色，基础设施用浅绿色。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "user",
        "computer",
        "group",
        "infrastructure",
        "classDef"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Domain Users虽然是普通组，但在实际评估里我们经常把它标红强调，因为它往往是权限扩散的起点。能加个特殊的admin组样式吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DOMAINUSERS",
        "admingroup"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加了admingroup样式，红色描边加粗。把Domain Users应用上去了。另外预留了certificate样式，万一后面要加证书相关节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "admingroup",
        "certificate",
        "DOMAINUSERS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才口误了——Domain Users是普通域组，不是真正的管理组。红色应该留给Domain Admins那种高敏感组。要不要先去掉？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DOMAINUSERS",
        "DOMAINADMINS",
        "admingroup"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "明白了，我把Domain Users改回普通group样式。不过admingroup样式我先留着，注释里提到了DOMAINADMINS，万一后续要扩展。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DOMAINUSERS",
