    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以。节点标签的格式也确认下：要显示FQDN、对象类型、还有具体分类，比如ALICE@PHANTOM.Corp下面标注User和Domain User。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ALICE",
        "LAPTOP",
        "PHANTOM",
